import os
import sys
import fastavro
import tarfile
import pprint
import socket

tarfile_nazov = './cloud/2019/1.tar'

tar = tarfile.open(tarfile_nazov)
f = open("cz-whitelist.cidr", "w")
for member in tar:
    if member.isfile and member.name.endswith('.avro'):
        avro_fd = tar.extractfile(member)
        avro_reader = fastavro.reader(avro_fd)
        sys.stdout.write('Skumanie {} \n'.format(member.name))
        sys.stdout.flush()
        
        f.write('#Czech MX servers based on the OpenIntel dataset\n')
        for record in avro_reader:
            qtype = record['response_type']
            domena = record['query_name'].lower()
            if qtype == 'MX' and domena.endswith('.cz.'):
                mx_addr = record['mx_address']
                try:
                    ip_addr = socket.gethostbyname(mx_addr)
                except:
                    print('Chybný MX záznam, alebo záznam chýba')                     
                print(' ({} - {} - {})'.format(domena, mx_addr, ip_addr))  
                f.write(ip_addr+'\tPERMIT\n')  
tar.close()
f.close()
sys.stdout.write('Done...')
